msgstr "``LinearElasticityMultiFrequency``\\ （以及 ``…3D``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:210
#: 575fa01e6a914e49a973972e3bf7cf3c
msgid ""
"Each ``…MultiFrequency`` class samples random Fourier coefficients for the "
"source term and -- where applicable -- returns the analytical solution at "
"the same nodes, which is convenient for both training and validation."
msgstr "每个 ``…MultiFrequency`` 类都会为源项采样随机傅里叶系数，并在适用时返回相同节点上的解析解，这对训练和验证都很方便。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:215
#: 29ada88b250c40ccb54696e5a9163267
msgid ""
"The standard \"same mesh, varying source\" recipe combines this generator "
"with the batched-RHS pattern from Axis 2:"
msgstr "标准的“同一网格、变化源项”方案，将这个生成器与维度 2 的批量右端项模式结合起来："

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:240
#: 55da14ad545344a7a9f7f27808e1da6a
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"On a single RTX PRO 6000 the loop above produces 1024 Poisson solutions in "
"roughly 34 ms (see the throughput figure above) -- about "
":math:`30\\,\\mu\\mathrm{s}` per problem, dominated by the cuDSS triangular "
"back-substitution. The fully benchmarked driver, with timing across many "
"``n_batch`` values, lives in "
"``examples/dataset/poisson/poisson_dataset.py``."
msgstr ""
"在单块 RTX PRO 6000 上，上面的循环大约用 34 ms 产生 1024 个泊松解（见上方的吞吐量图）——每个问题约 "
":math:`30\\,\\mu\\mathrm{s}`\\ ，主要耗时在 cuDSS 的三角回代上。完整基准测试的驱动脚本（含跨多个 "
"``n_batch`` 取值的计时）位于 ``examples/dataset/poisson/poisson_dataset.py``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:247
#: 4fa59ee789f0403b91d084d5db9feb1b
msgid ""
"For *varying mesh* workflows, regenerate ``Mesh`` per problem and pay the "
"assembly cost each time -- there is no shortcut for that case today."
msgstr "对于\\ *网格变化*\\ 的工作流，需要为每个问题重新生成 ``Mesh`` 并每次都付出装配开销——目前这种情况没有捷径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:255
#: 539b2413043049f4b478685a3a648548
msgid "What's not built in"
msgstr "尚未内置的功能"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:257
#: c2a7232defc047c58f277708649f7b73
msgid ""
"There is **no** built-in vmap-style assembler that vectorises ``K`` "
"construction across many parameter values (e.g. one ``K`` per realisation of"
" a stochastic coefficient field). For now two patterns work in user code:"
msgstr ""
"目前\\ **没有**\\ 内置的 vmap 式装配器来跨多个参数取值对 ``K`` 的构造进行向量化（例如为随机系数场的每一次实现生成一个 "
"``K``\\ ）。当下，用户代码中有两种可行模式："

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:262
#: a0d0b4eb163942be927fd80d9ed4c183
msgid ""
"**Python loop** -- simplest, fine when assembly is cheap relative to solve."
msgstr "**Python 循环**——最简单，当装配相对于求解开销较小时完全够用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:264
#: 7d02d88a0be843a281dc4a5981e2c9e1
msgid ""
"**``torch.vmap`` around the assembler call** -- works when the varying "
"parameter enters via ``point_data`` or ``element_data`` and the result is "
"uniform in shape. Note that ``vmap``'s interaction with sparse output is "
"fragile; test on small problems first."
msgstr ""
"**用 ``torch.vmap`` 包住装配器调用**——当变化的参数通过 ``point_data`` 或 ``element_data`` "
"传入、且结果形状一致时可用。请注意 ``vmap`` 与稀疏输出的配合较为脆弱；请先在小问题上测试。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:270
#: b09063bdb0b2494a9ea0869afe3f88fd
msgid ""
"A first-class batched-assembly API may show up in a future release; the "
"dataset workflow above covers the most common case (same mesh, many sources)"
" without it."
msgstr "未来的某个版本可能会出现一等公民级别的批量装配 API；即便没有它，上文的数据集工作流也已涵盖了最常见的情形（同一网格、多个源项）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:276
#: 994e9b584f8c4a78b774cdd5695975fd
msgid "Reproducing the numbers"
msgstr "复现这些数据"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:278
#: f39c9a90c0c9413fa3be4b32700d8253
msgid "All three figures on this page come from a single script:"
msgstr "本页的三幅图均来自同一个脚本："

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:284
#: af844fa397aa4e848e05be13ac69c3b4
msgid ""
"It uses only the public API and runs on CPU alone (the GPU panels are "
"skipped on a CPU-only machine). On a CUDA host it writes "
"``batched_rhs_scaling.png``, ``throughput.png``, and ``memory_chunking.png``"
" into ``docs/source/_static/user_guide/batched_workflows/``."
msgstr ""
"它仅使用公开 API，且可仅在 CPU 上运行（在纯 CPU 机器上会跳过 GPU 相关的图）。在 CUDA 主机上，它会将 "
"``batched_rhs_scaling.png``\\ 、\\ ``throughput.png`` 和 "
"``memory_chunking.png`` 写入 "
"``docs/source/_static/user_guide/batched_workflows/``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/batched_workflows.rst:292
#: 996254a5ca194ebd9e22f7a7eed7bcb8
msgid "What's next"
msgstr "下一步"

